du festival : la course de relais.

676
00:48:02,025 --> 00:48:05,070
Village de Deokpung 2 !

677
00:48:18,750 --> 00:48:21,878
Allons-y, village de Deokpung 2 !

678
00:48:26,842 --> 00:48:27,676
Merci.

679
